OASISFormat: 0.4
OCamlVersion: >= 3.12.0
Name: gapi-ocaml
Version: 0.3.1
LicenseFile: LICENSE
License: MIT
BuildType: ocamlbuild (0.4)
Authors: Alessandro Strada
Maintainers: Alessandro Strada <alessandro.strada@gmail.com>
